美又想收多條共產黨暴政下既死屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447956126e1d61e92c425d3e86cc3fe2e6423ba3","tid":299193,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:14:29.000Z","msg":"癌細胞擴散到多個器官<br />\n<br />\n做乜都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ff57e7836c0e10b6075f06baf561538ae941df","tid":299193,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"肝can, 仲要末期, 邊有得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}